dialog:
lt has fallen into the hands of 
    the Elves. Everyone will try to claim it: Men, Dwarves, wizards. We cannot 
    let that happen. This thing must come to Gondor.,

What would you have me do? Look at my men. Their courage hangs by a 
    thread. If this is to be our end, then I would have them make such an 
    end......as to be worthy of remembrance.,

Bru-ra-hroom.
There have been no Entings
for a terrible long count of years.,

I'm starving.
We ain't had nothing but maggoty bread
for three stinking days.,
